title: Minority Representation in the Parliament of Lybia 1
summary: This chart shows how the 1 of Minority in the Parliament Lybia Parliament has changed over the Years .
\n It shows that between 1990 - 1994 there was a 0.4 percentage Minority which increased gradually over the Years .

Between 1995 - 1999 the Minority was at 2.1 percentage , 2000 - 2004 it was 7.4 percentage , 2005 - 2009 it was 10.0 percentage , 2010 - 2014 it was 12.6 percentage and between 2015 - 2019 Minority was at its highest at 14.0 percentage .
gold: Minority representation in the Parliament of lybia has steadily increased between the years 1990 and 2019 . between 1990 and 1994 it was approximately 0.4 % and in the years 2015 and 2019 it was approximately 14 % .
